Package javelin.model.diplomacy.mandate

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Mandate
    A Diplomacy action.
    RequestAlly
    Adds a non-mercenary Combatant to a Squad inside the Town District.
    RequestGold
    Adds gold to a Squad standing in the respective District.
    RequestLocation
    Requests that one or more undiscovered Actors be revealed.
    RequestMap
    Reveals area around a District.
    RequestTrade
    Connects a ResourceSite.Resource from a town that has it to a town that doesn't.
    RevealAlignment
    Reveals a Town's Alignment.ethics.
